{"tid":2122353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"胡錫進：中國若不反制  防線就有可能崩潰！","createTime":"2020-07-24T03:04:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T03:32:02.000Z","uid":7542,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ef305d0200e8c98bcbda1de079335e6adb7decda","tid":2122353,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:04:18.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><br />\n好心拉佢去打靶啦<br />\n計我話中國係永世不倒</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內地《環球時報》總編輯胡錫進透露，在美國強行要求關閉中國駐休斯敦總領館之後，中方今天將宣布對美國的反制措施，據他了解，將有一間美國在華總領館被對等要求關閉。<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進形容，<strong>這是中國不得不採取的措施，國際關係的基本規則和外交事務的對等準則，要求中方必須做出這樣的反應，否則中國作為大國的信譽，將捅出一個大窿，應對複雜局面的防線有可能崩潰</strong>。胡錫進相信，中國的專業外交團隊經過充分評估，才形成應對方案，並選定報復目標，又說與美國的鬥爭高度複雜，相信這個團隊會高度忠誠，選擇最好或者最不壞的策略，幫助中國應對不同尋常的挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539605-20200724.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539605-20200724.htm&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6Pkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=439e2b53\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539605-20200724.htm&h=be7d133c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539605-20200724.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1a90f476f2ff6768af7b6fc5a48fe69c288efaf3","tid":2122353,"uid":151074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:06:02.000Z","msg":"胡某：有啲驚，燈一燈自己嗰邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baf1c80af0ed54f0028cfa484aaffa056ff06e50","tid":2122353,"uid":361247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ef305d0200e8c98bcbda1de079335e6adb7decda","tid":2122353,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:04:18.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><br />\n好心拉佢去打靶啦<br />\n計我話中國係永世不倒</strong></span><img src=\"/